<lb n="0401a24"/><p>此&CB00057;隨誦即成。一日三時一一時中誦一百
<lb n="0401a25"/>八遍。能得除滅五逆重罪及諸業障。燒沈水
<lb n="0401a26"/>香欲結界時。或&CB00057;水或&CB00057;灰。或&CB00057;芥子或&CB00057;
<lb n="0401a27"/>紫檀木四枚。各七遍釘於四方。一切<note n="0401014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">瘧＋（病）【三】</note><note n="0401014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">瘧＋（病）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401014"><lem>瘧</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">瘧病</rdg></app>寒熱
<lb n="0401a28"/>病。作&CB00057;索誦二十一遍繫其<note n="0401015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">咽＝胭【三】＊</note><note n="0401015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">咽＝胭【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0401015"><lem>咽</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">胭</rdg></app>下。即得除愈
<lb n="0401a29"/>一切諸病。或&CB00057;<note n="0401016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">酥＝蘇【宋】</note><app n="0401016"><lem>酥</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">蘇</rdg></app>或&CB00057;油或&CB00057;水。各二十一
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1093.0401b" n="0401b"/>
<lb n="0401b01"/>遍&CB00057;已服之。若欲破他所作&CB00057;<note n="0401017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">咀＝詛【元】【明】</note><app n="0401017"><lem>咀</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">詛</rdg></app>。作其人形
<lb n="0401b02"/>像。或麵或<note n="0401018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00410;＝泥【三】</note><note n="0401018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00410;＝泥【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401018"><lem>&CB00410;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">泥</rdg></app>或<note n="0401019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蠟＝臘【三】</note><note n="0401019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蠟＝臘【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401019"><lem>蠟</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">臘</rdg></app>。當以<note n="0401020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鑌＝賓【宋】</note><app n="0401020"><lem>鑌</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">賓</rdg></app>鐵為刀段段割
<lb n="0401b03"/>之。若有人驚怖欲護身者。當作&CB00057;索帶於身
<lb n="0401b04"/>上。若有人患腹痛。&CB00057;鹹水服之。若有人被蟲
<lb n="0401b05"/>毒或被蛇螫。當用<note n="0401021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">塗＝泥【三】＊</note><note n="0401021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">塗＝泥【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0401021"><lem>塗</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">泥</rdg></app>&CB00057;塗之。若有人患眼
<lb n="0401b06"/>痛。取白<note n="0401022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">綖＝線【三】＊</note><note n="0401022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">綖＝線【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0401022"><lem>綖</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">線</rdg></app>為&CB00057;索繫其耳上。若人患齒。取
<lb n="0401b07"/>迦羅毘羅木<note n="0401023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00057;＋（之）【三】</note><note n="0401023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00057;＋（之）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401023"><lem>&CB00057;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB00057;之</rdg></app>二十一遍。然後嚼之揩磨其
<lb n="0401b08"/>齒。欲作大界。取五色<app type="＊" source="0401022"><lem>綖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">線</rdg></app>&CB00057;二十一遍。取紫
<lb n="0401b09"/>檀木四枚為&CB02000;繫索於&CB02000;上纏之。釘著四角
<lb n="0401b10"/>即成大界。一者怖處一切驚處欲護身者。當
<lb n="0401b11"/>作&CB00057;索帶行。或&CB00057;水灑之或&CB00057;灰用散其上。
<lb n="0401b12"/>若有鬼著取五色<app type="＊" source="0401022"><lem>綖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">線</rdg></app>為&CB00057;索帶之或繫身體。
<lb n="0401b13"/>一切寒熱病者。取白<app type="＊" source="0401022"><lem>綖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">線</rdg></app>&CB00057;二十一遍作索帶
<lb n="0401b14"/>行。若有得一切種種惡瘡。取<note n="0401024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蓽茇＝畢&CB03247;【宋】</note><app n="0401024"><lem>蓽茇</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">畢&CB03247;</rdg></app>擣以為末
<lb n="0401b15"/>和蜜。&CB00057;二十一遍<note n="0401025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">泥＝塗【三】＊</note><note n="0401025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">泥＝塗【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0401025"><lem>泥</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">塗</rdg></app>其瘡上。若有人患眼。取
<lb n="0401b16"/>香湯或甘草湯。&CB00057;二十一遍洗兩眼。若有人
<lb n="0401b17"/>患耳。煮油&CB00057;二十一遍內著耳中。一切&CB00508;諍
<lb n="0401b18"/>一切官府一切恐怖處。取水&CB00057;二十一遍洗
<lb n="0401b19"/>其面。若國內有大疫病。或城邑聚落。乃至家
<lb n="0401b20"/>內當作道場。牛糞<app type="＊" source="0401021"><lem>塗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">泥</rdg></app>地香湯灑地。於四角處
<lb n="0401b21"/>安置新淨水瓶。以種種華置其瓶&M034294;。復將種
<lb n="0401b22"/>種華散道場處。持種種飲食皆令香美。復以
<lb n="0401b23"/>種種淨草敷設道場。以食置上并諸果蓏。於
<lb n="0401b24"/>四角處麵作燈盞。淨布作炷燒諸妙香。以最
<lb n="0401b25"/>勝<note n="0401026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上者＝最大【三】</note><note n="0401026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">上者＝最大【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401026"><lem>上者</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">最大</rdg></app>而作供養。<note n="0401027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔其&CB00057;師〕－【三】</note><note n="0401027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔其&CB00057;師〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401027"><lem>其&CB00057;師</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>以香湯澡浴著
<lb n="0401b26"/>鮮淨衣。於其座上敷新淨褥而坐其上。誦持
<lb n="0401b27"/>此&CB00057;一切災變即得消滅。若有遇重病者。將
<lb n="0401b28"/>彼瓶水&CB00057;已灑於彼人。凡所灑者即得除滅
<lb n="0401b29"/>一切疫病。諸鬼<note n="0401028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">崇＝祟【三】</note><note n="0401028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">崇＝祟【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401028"><lem>崇</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">祟</rdg></app>者一切有怖畏處。以水灑
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1093.0401c" n="0401c"/>
<lb n="0401c01"/>之皆得除愈。若有人被他禁&CB00057;。磨栴檀&CB00057;二
<lb n="0401c02"/>十一遍。<app type="＊" source="0401025"><lem>泥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">塗</rdg></app>其心上即得除愈。若欲除滅一切
<lb n="0401c03"/>業障及五逆四重。常誦莫住。若有家內遇<note n="0401029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">疫＝惡疾【三】</note><note n="0401029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">疫＝惡疾【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401029"><lem>疫</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">惡疾</rdg></app>
<lb n="0401c04"/>病。或復諸鬼<note n="0401030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">擾＝繞【宋】，撓【元】【明】</note><note n="0401030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">擾＝繞【宋】，＝撓【元】【明】</note><app n="0401030"><lem>擾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">繞</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">撓</rdg></app>亂其家。當取一百八枚蓮華。
<lb n="0401c05"/>一一蓮華各&CB00057;一遍。擲著火中即得除愈。若
<lb n="0401c06"/>欲取一切眾生心意。當取栴檀一百八枚長
<lb n="0401c07"/>二寸。一枚一遍&CB00057;之擲著火中。欲治一切鬼
<lb n="0401c08"/>病恐怖之處。當取闍耶草<note n="0401031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔藉草根〕－【三】</note><note n="0401031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔藉草根〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401031"><lem><note place="inline">藉草根</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>毘闍耶草<note n="0401032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔藥〕－【三】＊</note><note n="0401032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔藥〕－【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0401032"><lem><note place="inline">藥</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0401c09"/>那句利<app type="＊" source="0401032"><lem><note place="inline">藥</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>揵陀那句<note n="0401033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">梨＝利【三】</note><note n="0401033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">梨＝利【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401033"><lem>梨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">利</rdg></app>草<app type="＊" source="0401032"><lem><note place="inline">藥</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0400010"><lem>這</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">適</rdg></app>憐尼草<app type="＊" source="0401032"><lem><note place="inline">藥</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0401c10"/>阿婆耶波&CB00135;草<app type="＊" source="0401032"><lem><note place="inline">藥</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>因陀羅波尼草<note n="0401034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">香附子三字三本俱作本文</note><note n="0401034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（香附子）三字夾註＝（香附子）三字本文【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401034"><lem><note place="inline">香附子</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">香附子</rdg></app>多迦
<lb n="0401c11"/>羅<note n="0401035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">香字三本俱作本文下同</note><note n="0401035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（香）夾註＝（香）本文【宋】下同【元】下同【明】下同</note><app n="0401035"><lem><note place="inline">香</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">香</rdg></app>斫迦羅<note place="inline">香</note>摩<note n="0401036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訶＝呵【三】</note><note n="0401036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訶＝呵【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401036"><lem>訶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">呵</rdg></app>斫迦羅<note place="inline">香</note>毘疏&CB03905;揵多<note place="inline">香</note>
<lb n="0401c12"/>蘇摩<note n="0401037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅＝囉【三】</note><note n="0401037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">羅＝囉【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401037"><lem>羅</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">囉</rdg></app><note n="0401038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔是梔子〕－【三】</note><note n="0401038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔是梔子〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401038"><lem><note place="inline">是梔子</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0401039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（多草）＋蘇【三】</note><note n="0401039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（多草）＋蘇【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401039"><lem>蘇</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">多草蘇</rdg></app>難陀<note n="0401040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">草字三本俱作本文</note><note n="0401040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（草）夾註＝（草）本文【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401040"><lem><note place="inline">草</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">草</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0401c13"/><p>如是諸草。皆搗之作末細羅之。取水和為丸
<lb n="0401c14"/>如大棗。&CB00057;一百八遍。或頭戴或繫手而行。一
<lb n="0401c15"/>切鬼病一切疫病不能為害。若有小兒著鬼
<lb n="0401c16"/>病及疫病所驚怖處。將一丸繫於<app type="＊" source="0401015"><lem>咽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">胭</rdg></app>下。若有
<lb n="0401c17"/>女人薄相難嫁娶者或有諸病。取此丸藥和
<lb n="0401c18"/>水澡浴。即除惡相<note n="0401041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">最妙最勝＝最勝最妙【三】</note><note n="0401041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">最妙最勝＝最勝最妙【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401041"><lem>最妙最勝</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">最勝最妙</rdg></app>隨意無難。若有
<lb n="0401c19"/>女人不生男者。持藥一丸繫其項即得產男。
<lb n="0401c20"/>一切驚怖中皆作大護。若有人被蟲者。此藥
<lb n="0401c21"/>亦能破之。帶藥行者不被火燒諸難。若被惡
<lb n="0401c22"/>瘡。持此藥塗者<note n="0401042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">即＝則【三】</note><note n="0401042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">即＝則【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401042"><lem>即</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">則</rdg></app>得除<note n="0401043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">差＝瘥【三】</note><note n="0401043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">差＝瘥【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401043"><lem>差</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">瘥</rdg></app>。若有人為諸惡
<lb n="0401c23"/>事逼切。帶此藥者即蒙除難。若有人欲除惡
<lb n="0401c24"/>風惡雨。&CB00057;水二十一遍散於四方。即得除止。
<lb n="0401c25"/>若遇大雹。取一樹枝行&CB00057;遙打之。此觀世音
<lb n="0401c26"/>心&CB00057;雖不受持。但誦能破一切業障。能成一
<lb n="0401c27"/>切事皆得成就。若有人持此&CB00057;者。彼人當織
<lb n="0401c28"/><note n="0401044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一＋（端）【三】</note><note n="0401044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一＋（端）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401044"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">一端</rdg></app>白&CB00626;。闊五尺長一丈不得割斷。綜縷彼&CB00626;
<lb n="0401c29"/>當畫作一佛。<note n="0401045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">綵＝像采【三】</note><note n="0401045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">綵＝像采【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401045"><lem>綵</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">像采</rdg></app>色中不得用膠。當和香<note n="0401046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">及乳和綵色＝水及以乳汁而用【三】</note><note n="0401046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">及乳和綵色＝水及以乳汁而用【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401046"><lem>及
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1093.0402a" n="0402a"/>
<lb n="0402a01"/>乳和綵色</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">水及以乳汁而用</rdg></app>畫之。右邊畫作觀世音像。狀如摩
<lb n="0402a02"/>醯首羅天。頭上<note n="0402001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">髮＋（毛）【三】</note><note n="0402001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">髮＋（毛）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0402001"><lem>髮</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">髮毛</rdg></app>悉如<note n="0402002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00657;＝螺【三】</note><note n="0402002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00657;＝螺【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0402002"><lem>&CB00657;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">螺</rdg></app>髻。方作華冠。肩
<lb n="0402a03"/>上當畫作黑鹿皮覆左肩上。自餘身分當畫
<lb n="0402a04"/>作種種瓔珞。其畫者教持八關齋勿得雜食。
<lb n="0402a05"/>日別香湯清淨澡浴著淨衣裳。其持&CB00057;者當
<lb n="0402a06"/>清淨處安像。像前以牛糞塗地。四方齊整縱
<lb n="0402a07"/>廣丈六尺。其壇場&M034294;散純白華。置八水瓶各
<lb n="0402a08"/>受一斗。皆令新淨盛以香湯。復以種種華置
<lb n="0402a09"/>其瓶內。安其淨草立八草<note n="0402003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">座＋（座）【三】</note><note n="0402003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">座＋（座）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0402003"><lem>座</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">座座</rdg></app>處。安置八方作
<lb n="0402a10"/>八分食置其草座上。然後更以六十四分食。
<lb n="0402a11"/>各各種種雜美好者。自餘雜食具皆廣大<note n="0402004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔羅列〕－【三】</note><note n="0402004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔羅列〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0402004"><lem>羅
<lb n="0402a12"/>列</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>作之。<note n="0402005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唯＝惟【三】</note><note n="0402005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯＝惟【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0402005"><lem>唯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">惟</rdg></app>除五辛酒肉。餘但使可得之者皆
<lb n="0402a13"/>悉具之。若欲&CB00057;者。當三日三夜斷食燒沈水
<lb n="0402a14"/>香。其持&CB00057;<note n="0402006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">人＝者【三】</note><note n="0402006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">人＝者【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0402006"><lem>人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">者</rdg></app>以妙香湯三時澡<note n="0402007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">洗＝洒【三】</note><note n="0402007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">洗＝洒【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0402007"><lem>洗</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">洒</rdg></app>。大小便
<lb n="0402a15"/>時皆須澡浴。若不能三日三夜者。但一日一
<lb n="0402a16"/>夜斷食。當食三種白食乳酪粳米。在彼像前
<lb n="0402a17"/>長跪設飲食已。當誦&CB00057;一千八遍。爾時<note n="0402008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔行者〕－【三】</note><note n="0402008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔行者〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0402008"><lem>行者</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0402a18"/>在於像前。即見自身出大光明猶如火焰。既
<lb n="0402a19"/>自見已生大歡欣。乃至觀世音菩薩自來現
<lb n="0402a20"/>身。隨其心願皆悉與之。若欲隱身。當取雌黃
<lb n="0402a21"/>或石黛。擣令碎末精細羅之。在於像前&CB00057;一
<lb n="0402a22"/>千八遍。塗於眼上即得隱身。乃至騰空飛行。
<lb n="0402a23"/>復得三昧名不空智<note n="0402009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">見＝現【三】</note><note n="0402009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">見＝現【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0402009"><lem>見</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">現</rdg></app>在莊嚴。作如是法已。
<lb n="0402a24"/>然後凡所作者皆得成就。此是持&CB00057;法我今
<lb n="0402a25"/>說竟</p>
<lb n="0402a26"/><p>爾時佛說此經已。時觀世音菩薩摩訶薩。及
<lb n="0402a27"/>淨居諸天子娑婆世界主大梵天王。及諸菩
<lb n="0402a28"/>薩眾諸聲聞眾一切大眾人民。聞觀世音菩
<lb n="0402a29"/>薩對佛說此經。皆大歡喜奉行</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1093.0402b" n="0402b"/>
